review: These are Good cables at a good price!! Not sure they would hold up to heavy use, but for practicing at home they are really great!
These are great guitar straps at a very reasonable price!! I bought 2 to try them out, and I intend on buying more!!
This is a very GOOD General purpose strap! A little stiff, but I'm hoping it will loosen up with use.
These are really great guitar locks!! I use them on all my guitars, and I would highly recommend them to anyone!!
These are really well made straps for the money! The only problem I had was that I wished I had ordered more of them!!!!
